the group had to carry out three creative tasks: First, the group had to develop the official program for the so-called Cultural EventWeek at the university (Task 0). Second, they had to develop the timetable for that particular week (Task 1) and, finally, they had to design the posters that would be used to promote theCultural EventsWeek (Task 2)

After finishing tasks 1 and 2, participants filled in a self-report questionnaire with the study variables

