observers with greater levels of empathetic reactions will be more drawn into the group (cf., Konvalinka et al., 2011; Xygalatas et al., 2013) and biologically related observers will be likely to experience strong emotional reactions to the display of ordeal (Konvalinka et al., 2011; Fischer et al., 2014)

