RM: You must concentrate on what you are reading; each word is worth a thousand pieces of gold. (29)

In order for FPFSL to prevail, scholarly education is necessary as part of the concern of loyalty to self–other interpersonal relationship. A basic concern of parents is to prevent the family from being ruined, and this prevention is directly seen to be based on the education of their children

If parents neglected the education of their children, they would feel ashamed or guilty, because they would lose their money and grain or official positions symbolized by ‘official costume and hat.'

CCMF 3 (1): [children worth instructing {\textgreater}|{\textless} saying they know nothing].

CCMF 3 (2): [concentration on reading {\textgreater}|{\textless} each word worth 10,000 pieces of gold].


4. Strong WIll: Stoicism? 

AM: Not until the sheaths have fallen off can a bamboo shoot become a bamboo; not until it has rushed about can the fish become a dragon. (146)

IM: As long as there are green poplar trees to attach the horse, there are roads everywhere leading to the capital city of Chang'an. (309)

