This involves trying to sanction off culture from its ecological niche (Laland {\&} Hoppitt 2003).  What about the cultural forms that are distributed in socio-technical environments and indeed the fact that many of the abstract processes of human culture/cognition are shaped by specific ecologies (cultural diversity)?  (Roepstorff 2010, Kirsch 2006).  
        
